data.description: Don't miss this beautiful brick home located in Chester. This gorgeous 1500 squarefoot 3 bed 2 bath home is a must see. Sitting on a beautiful 1.54 acres, this home is surrounded by pecan and an assortment of fruit trees. Inside features new flooring, paint and fixtures. A spacious living area offers plenty of room for family gatherings. The front and back yard are both fenced in with new chain link fencing.
